<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>204</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 duō shǎo nián de qí dǎo, zhōng yú zǒu dào jīn tiān,
 suǒ yǒu rén de jiǎo bù dōu zǒu dào tóng yī gè qǐ diǎn.
 duō shǎo nián de bēn bō, yī tóng zǒu guò fēng hé yǔ,
 shǒu wǎn shǒu jiān bìng jiān liú xià dié yìn de zú jī.
 wèi fú yīn yī shēng wú huǐ,
 shì kǔ shì lè wǒ men yī zhí yào zǒu xià qù.
 wèi fú yīn yī shēng wú huǐ,
 huò dōng huò xī wǒ men yuàn yì xiàn shàng zì jǐ.</lyrics>
<title>wèi fú yīn yī shēng wú huǐ 迦南204</title>
</song>